room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Just Escape in New York
review: My son and his friends did the underworld room. They had a blast.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Just Escape in New York
review: We had a fun and exciting experience in The Underworld. Great night out filled with lots laughs. Perfect idea for an adult night out!

room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Just Escape in New York
review: We came for my birthday yesterday it was so much fun!! We made it out with minutes to spare. Best escape room I've done yet! We did Underworld.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Just Escape in New York
review: My friends and I did the Underworld Room in the Massapequa location tonight along with a couple that joined us. So much fun and laughs. The clues given were helpful but still challenging. Highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Just Escape in New York
review: We chose the Underworld room in Massapequa. Lots of fun! Our game master was great as well!
